      "content": "what do you mean by \"letting go\"? it feels like there's nothing left to let go of. i've tried everything. i've tried changing jobs, therapy, being alone, being around people... it always comes back to this same place. i'm just lying here thinking that the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... end it. to make it stop for good. does that even make sense?",
